1
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:36,280
=Side Story Of Fox Volant=
(Adapted from Jin Yong's novel)

2
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,700
=Episode 12=

3
00:01:40,330 --> 00:01:41,690
Step aside!

4
00:01:45,260 --> 00:01:45,930
Renfeng.

5
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:48,370
What you see

6
00:01:48,770 --> 00:01:50,100
isn't what you think it is.

7
00:01:50,450 --> 00:01:51,770
I can explain it...

8
00:01:58,940 --> 00:01:59,620
Leader Tian.

9
00:01:59,940 --> 00:02:00,660
Go away!

10
00:02:04,050 --> 00:02:04,890
Alright.

11
00:02:05,980 --> 00:02:08,460
To die by the world's
best swordmaster's hand,

12
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:09,690
I, Tian Guinong,

13
00:02:10,170 --> 00:02:11,300
have no regrets.

14
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:12,370
Come on!

15
00:02:16,770 --> 00:02:17,540
Stop!

16
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:27,540
This is between me and him.

17
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:28,690
It's between you and me.

18
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:37,940
Let me finish what I have to say.

19
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:40,490
Then you can do as you wish.

20
00:02:43,970 --> 00:02:46,060
We really thought
you had died in Miaojiang.

21
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:46,610
Otherwise...

22
00:02:46,610 --> 00:02:47,420
You shut up.

23
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:53,730
Miao Renfeng.

24
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,780
Be honest.

25
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:02,330
Did you ever really love me?

26
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,860
Have you ever cared about me?

27
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:09,500
If I were the sword in your hand,

28
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:12,780
I'd at least get
more attention from you.

29
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:16,300
But you only cared about
the martial world and your friends,

30
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:18,610
and the promise you made
to Hu Yidao and his wife.

31
00:03:19,890 --> 00:03:21,220
I'm a woman.

32
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,730
I only wished for you to be with me.

33
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:28,140
So I wouldn't have to always worry.

34
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:30,780
So I wouldn't have
to watch the empty house.

35
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:33,970
I'm grateful to you
for saving my life back then.

36
00:03:34,970 --> 00:03:36,420
I once thought

37
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,860
I'd grow old with you.

38
00:03:40,090 --> 00:03:41,420
Later I realized

39
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:45,610
you didn't need a wife or family.

40
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:48,020
You're living in your own world,

41
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,100
doing as you please.

42
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:51,860
You're not willing to change for me.

43
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:55,380
It's the same when Ruolan came along.

44
00:03:56,170 --> 00:03:57,100
If so,

45
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:01,490
then why keep me by your side?

46
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:06,610
Is this how you see me?

47
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:08,330
How else am I supposed to see you?

48
00:04:10,210 --> 00:04:12,380
Even when Ruolan got a fever today,

49
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:14,770
you weren't there.

50
00:04:24,650 --> 00:04:26,260
I've finished what I wanted to say.

51
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:30,930
Go on then.

52
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,540
I will never give up the promise

53
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,490
I made to Hu Yidao.

54
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:09,100
If you're willing to stay,

55
00:05:10,890 --> 00:05:12,650
I will protect you forever.

56
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:18,380
Let us go home.

57
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:20,490
Okay?

58
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:53,140
♪Let youth blow your long hair♪

59
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:56,580
♪And pull your dreams away♪

60
00:05:58,060 --> 00:06:01,900
♪Unwittingly the city's history♪

61
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:05,700
♪Has recorded your smile♪

62
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:10,500
♪The azure sky in the red heart♪

63
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:14,460
♪Sets a beginning of life♪

64
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:17,730
♪You stayed up during
the rainy spring nights♪

65
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:19,580
If you have nowhere to go,

66
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:21,370
♪Of the days of sleeping alone♪

67
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,770
will you stay with me?

68
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:25,260
I'll hold you like a pearl in my hand,

69
00:06:25,770 --> 00:06:27,020
protecting you forever.

70
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:32,260
♪Blossom to show its secret beauty♪

71
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:33,410
♪The catkins floating here and there♪

72
00:06:33,410 --> 00:06:35,770
I know you have a promise to keep.

73
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,740
And I know your words
mean everything to you.

74
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:38,890
I know the reasoning.

75
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:40,290
♪Are illusions for your smiley face♪

76
00:06:40,290 --> 00:06:41,970
But I don't want you to go.

77
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:43,700
♪Seasons change♪

78
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,340
♪In this mortal world♪

79
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:49,340
♪Who decides fate♪

80
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:53,780
♪You were quiet on the cold snowy night♪

81
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:57,540
♪With your unconcealable gloss♪

82
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,140
♪Look at me♪

83
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,410
♪Just one more glance♪

84
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:06,010
♪Let not the beauty sleep alone♪

85
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:07,970
Come, get in the carriage.

86
00:07:07,970 --> 00:07:16,220
♪Youth regretless and immortal,
you're my lover forever♪

87
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:19,250
♪Let the wandering footprints
in the desert♪

88
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:19,940
Ride!

89
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:23,660
♪Write down the eternal memories♪

90
00:07:25,140 --> 00:07:28,980
♪The handwriting drifting to and fro♪

91
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:32,780
♪Is the hidden passion and words
dwelling in your heart♪

92
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:37,580
♪In the relentless reincarnations♪

93
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:41,540
♪Who's roaming amongst the echoes?♪

94
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:46,740
♪Laughing at my blind love
and solicitude♪

95
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:51,140
Once the Epiphyllum Dew Cream is made,

96
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:53,770
it has to be kept
in this cold jade container.

97
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,620
Otherwise, the efficacy

98
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,330
will dissipate within three days.

99
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:00,180
Supposedly, the old sage

100
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:02,140
tried to use other jade containers.

101
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,290
But none worked.

102
00:09:06,770 --> 00:09:08,180
This jade box is bone-chilling cold.

103
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,580
How mysterious.

104
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:12,770
It is said that this cold jade container

105
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:14,580
and the Epiphyllum Dew Cream

106
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:17,580
were given to Master Wuxiang
by the manifestation

107
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:18,850
of Buddha himself

108
00:09:18,850 --> 00:09:20,850
the day he founded the Sect.

109
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:23,140
Vedo Bodhisattva has already attained
his divination then.

110
00:09:23,530 --> 00:09:24,620
Meaning to say this jade box

111
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:26,330
isn't from the human world.

112
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,290
Lady Yuan.

113
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:32,410
You are now Weituo's leader.

114
00:09:32,410 --> 00:09:33,650
This jade box

115
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:36,210
will be yours to keep and use.

116
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:37,940
Now,

117
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,260
I will teach you how to operate it.

118
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:51,530
Weituo Sect's mechanism code

119
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:53,530
is Guanyin?

120
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:57,500
Don't you see the connection?

121
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:00,700
Do you mean

122
00:10:01,330 --> 00:10:03,090
the legend that Guanyin
and Vedo Bodhisattva

123
00:10:03,330 --> 00:10:05,330
were husband and wife?

124
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,220
Senior.

125
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,770
Will he soon recover after putting on

126
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:22,290
the Epiphyllum Dew Cream?

127
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,290
Change the dressing once a day.

128
00:10:24,290 --> 00:10:26,140
Do it continuously for seven days.

129
00:10:26,290 --> 00:10:28,290
The bone injury will heal.

130
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:31,140
Next, apply the Epiphyllum dew

131
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:33,690
to repair the damaged meridian.

132
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:35,220
Epiphyllum Dew?

133
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:36,690
To be more specific,

134
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:39,570
I'm now using
the Epiphyllum Dew Cream on him.

135
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:43,100
Its job is to heal the broken bones.

136
00:10:43,530 --> 00:10:45,140
You are a martial arts practitioner.

137
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,220
You should know

138
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,100
that once the meridian is damaged,

139
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:50,140
your skills can no longer improve.

140
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:53,980
The magical effect
of Epiphyllum Dew Cream

141
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:56,620
is its ability to repair
damaged meridians.

142
00:10:56,890 --> 00:10:59,620
Thus, you need to gather
fresh Epiphyllum dew

143
00:10:59,690 --> 00:11:02,050
and mix it together with the dream.

144
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:03,500
But I heard

145
00:11:03,890 --> 00:11:05,170
that the Epiphyllum is very scarce.

146
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:07,340
Don't you worry.

147
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:10,050
Weituo built its own garden,

148
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:12,340
specifically to plant Epiphyllum.

149
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:15,170
Once Young Hero Hu's injuries heal,

150
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:16,620
I'll get someone

151
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:18,620
to collect the Epiphyllum dew.

152
00:11:19,410 --> 00:11:20,410
Thank you, Senior.

153
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:26,690
The young man's fever has gone down.

154
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:28,770
Just get plenty of rest.

155
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,020
I can assure you

156
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:33,140
that you'll have him back all sprightly.

157
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:34,410
Senior...

158
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:44,890
Servant.

159
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,050
Get Madam...

160
00:11:46,050 --> 00:11:48,290
Get Lan some water.

161
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,500
Be good. Don't cry.

162
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:50,770
Take a seat, Lan.

163
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:51,620
Be good, Ruolan.

164
00:12:15,860 --> 00:12:16,810
Miao Renfeng!

165
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,140
Stop him!

166
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:34,460
(Tianlong)

167
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:37,480
(Tianlong)

168
00:13:10,050 --> 00:13:10,740
Step aside.

169
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:12,930
Miao Renfeng.

170
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:16,170
Come at me if you're frustrated.

171
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:17,620
Come at me!

172
00:13:17,890 --> 00:13:18,770
Don't take it out on them.

173
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:21,100
Don't make things hard for Nan Lan.

174
00:13:27,650 --> 00:13:28,770
It's me you're after.

175
00:13:29,690 --> 00:13:30,530
What do you want?

176
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:32,530
I won't hurt you.

177
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:35,460
Nor will I bother you again.

178
00:14:04,890 --> 00:14:05,570
Sorry.

179
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,650
Her name is Miao Ruolan.

180
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:13,860
Ruolan.

181
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:14,930
Ruolan!

182
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,570
Ruolan!

183
00:14:16,620 --> 00:14:17,690
Ruolan!

184
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:18,810
Let me go!

185
00:14:18,810 --> 00:14:21,980
Miao Renfeng, give me back Ruolan!

186
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,140
Ruolan!

187
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:24,860
Let me go!

188
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:28,290
Ruolan!

189
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:35,020
Ruolan!

190
00:14:36,050 --> 00:14:37,530
Ruolan!

191
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:40,220
Ruolan!

192
00:15:51,810 --> 00:15:52,620
You're awake.

193
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:55,220
How are you? Does it still hurt?

194
00:15:59,570 --> 00:16:00,810
Why didn't you wake me?

195
00:16:04,810 --> 00:16:06,380
You were smiling so sweetly.

196
00:16:07,170 --> 00:16:08,410
It must have been a good dream.

197
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:10,650
I couldn't bear to wake you up.

198
00:16:11,980 --> 00:16:12,650
So annoying.

199
00:16:13,570 --> 00:16:14,810
Why am I annoying?

200
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:17,020
I didn't do anything.

201
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,810
I just watched you.

202
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:20,260
I didn't say you could.

203
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:22,380
Next time, without my permission,

204
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:23,220
you're not allowed to look at me.

205
00:16:24,410 --> 00:16:25,770
Oh dear, that's not good.

206
00:16:26,650 --> 00:16:27,890
Because the moment I open my eyes,

207
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:29,500
I see only you.

208
00:16:31,690 --> 00:16:32,570
So cheeky.

209
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:34,980
Listen up.

210
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:38,140
If not for Weituo Sect,

211
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:40,050
your leg would've never healed.

212
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:42,620
Make sure you thank them properly.

213
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:44,020
Of course.

214
00:16:45,220 --> 00:16:47,020
I know the importance of gratitude.

215
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:53,810
What's so funny?

216
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:57,530
Now, when you're asleep,

217
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:58,930
you're so docile.

218
00:16:59,570 --> 00:17:01,860
Like a lazy cat sunbathing.

219
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:03,770
Why did you suddenly

220
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:05,860
become a little tiger after waking up?

221
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:08,020
Who's a little tiger?

222
00:17:08,690 --> 00:17:10,460
How rude. You called me a little tiger.

223
00:17:10,890 --> 00:17:11,620
Look.

224
00:17:11,930 --> 00:17:13,650
You're just like a little tiger.

225
00:17:13,650 --> 00:17:14,220
Hey...

226
00:17:19,410 --> 00:17:20,740
I... I just dropped by.

227
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:21,810
You two chat.

228
00:17:21,810 --> 00:17:23,100
I'm going to check the kitchen

229
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:24,260
to see if there's food.

230
00:17:24,260 --> 00:17:24,980
Senior.

231
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:25,980
I'll go to the kitchen.

232
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,570
Please check on him.

233
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:35,860
Lad, let's see how you're doing.

234
00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:37,260
Let me see.

235
00:18:03,170 --> 00:18:03,810
Chief Yuan.

236
00:18:04,690 --> 00:18:05,740
What would Young Hero Hu like to eat?

237
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:07,020
I'll get it prepared right away.

238
00:18:07,410 --> 00:18:08,050
That's alright.

239
00:18:08,930 --> 00:18:09,770
He just woke up.

240
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,290
He hasn't eaten in a while.

241
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,410
I'll make some porridge for him.

242
00:18:13,890 --> 00:18:14,500
Okay.

243
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,980
You're recovering well, lad.

244
00:18:20,340 --> 00:18:21,740
Make sure you eat.

245
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:23,020
It will help you heal.

246
00:18:24,770 --> 00:18:25,650
My leg.

247
00:18:26,530 --> 00:18:27,810
Thank you for saving it.

