00:30:41,610 --> 00:30:42,370
Alright.

500
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,420
Pardon me, Madam.

501
00:30:54,500 --> 00:30:56,500
How is it, doctor?

502
00:30:56,810 --> 00:30:58,220
Is Madam sick?

503
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,260
She almost fainted

504
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:00,740
out there just now.

505
00:31:06,220 --> 00:31:07,220
Madam is fine.

506
00:31:08,020 --> 00:31:10,090
She is pregnant.

507
00:31:11,130 --> 00:31:12,220
Congrats, Leader Tian.

508
00:31:13,020 --> 00:31:14,050
Congrats, Madam.

509
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:17,050
Congrats, Master and Madam.

510
00:31:56,810 --> 00:31:59,220
Why are you crying? This is happy news.

511
00:31:59,370 --> 00:32:00,980
I'm just overjoyed.

512
00:32:03,180 --> 00:32:03,740
Alright.

513
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:04,660
Okay.

514
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:06,090
Everyone's watching.

515
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:08,660
Gosh...

516
00:32:11,940 --> 00:32:13,090
You two

517
00:32:13,290 --> 00:32:15,260
are the madam's personal helpers.

518
00:32:16,090 --> 00:32:17,050
Now,

519
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:20,420
Madam is pregnant.

520
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:22,220
Make sure you look after her well

521
00:32:22,220 --> 00:32:23,500
and do whatever she asks.

522
00:32:23,810 --> 00:32:25,420
Make no mistake,

523
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:26,130
you hear?

524
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:27,180
Yes.

525
00:32:27,180 --> 00:32:28,130
Rest assured, Master.

526
00:32:28,130 --> 00:32:29,090
We will do our best

527
00:32:29,090 --> 00:32:31,530
to ensure madam is comfortable
and well looked after.

528
00:32:33,130 --> 00:32:34,020
You may go.

529
00:32:38,530 --> 00:32:40,460
Chief, everything is ready.

530
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:41,940
We can depart tomorrow.

531
00:32:42,220 --> 00:32:43,020
Tomorrow?

532
00:32:43,570 --> 00:32:44,290
That's so soon.

533
00:32:44,370 --> 00:32:46,180
You said it yourself. This matter is...

534
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:48,330
Sooner rather than later.

535
00:32:48,610 --> 00:32:50,460
Got it. You can go.

536
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:51,420
Yes, Sir.

537
00:33:19,530 --> 00:33:20,220
Look.

538
00:33:21,050 --> 00:33:21,810
Do you like it?

539
00:33:26,260 --> 00:33:27,940
This craftsmanship is exquisite.

540
00:33:28,330 --> 00:33:30,050
And the orchid looks very lifelike.

541
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:32,180
I like it.

542
00:33:34,850 --> 00:33:35,530
Let me.

543
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:55,900
The hairpin and hair
accentuate each other.

544
00:33:56,740 --> 00:34:00,180
But nothing beats the beauty
before the mirror.

545
00:34:03,460 --> 00:34:04,220
Guinong.

546
00:34:04,460 --> 00:34:06,050
You're always looking out for me.

547
00:34:06,570 --> 00:34:07,660
The free medicine and food

548
00:34:07,700 --> 00:34:09,420
have amounted to a lot of money.

549
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:10,700
Next time,

550
00:34:11,050 --> 00:34:12,660
don't waste more money on me.

551
00:34:13,290 --> 00:34:15,740
Money is just materialistic stuff.

552
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:17,850
I'm happy

553
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:19,260
as long as you're happy.

554
00:34:19,610 --> 00:34:20,330
Besides,

555
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:22,130
what you're doing are good deeds.

556
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,370
That's why the Tian Family

557
00:34:24,810 --> 00:34:25,980
received a blessing

558
00:34:26,530 --> 00:34:27,810
and got a child.

559
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:36,740
Nan Lan.

560
00:34:37,810 --> 00:34:39,370
There's something
I wish to discuss with you.

561
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,290
It's an urgent matter.

562
00:34:41,370 --> 00:34:42,700
I have to go to the capital
for a few days.

563
00:34:43,810 --> 00:34:44,700
When are you leaving?

564
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:45,660
Tomorrow.

565
00:34:45,810 --> 00:34:46,660
So soon?

566
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:51,500
If it wasn't so urgent,

567
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,370
I wouldn't wish to leave you now.

568
00:34:55,530 --> 00:34:56,180
But I worry...

569
00:34:56,180 --> 00:34:57,130
Just go without worry.

570
00:35:00,130 --> 00:35:00,810
Guinong.

571
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:02,220
Don't put your business on hold

572
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:03,770
because of me.

573
00:35:11,330 --> 00:35:12,660
This is what it means to have a wife.

574
00:35:14,290 --> 00:35:15,610
I ask for no more.

575
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:36,930
(Tianlong Sect)

576
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:47,130
Guinong.

577
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:50,090
Be safe on the way.

578
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:51,730
When it's dark,

579
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:53,340
find an inn to rest.

580
00:35:53,650 --> 00:35:54,690
Don't over-exert yourself.

581
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:56,650
Same for you.

582
00:35:57,050 --> 00:35:57,900
Don't overwork yourself.

583
00:35:58,090 --> 00:35:58,980
Remember.

584
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:00,690
There is another.

585
00:36:08,090 --> 00:36:09,210
Let the servants

586
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,730
handle the menial work.

587
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:11,980
Promise me

588
00:36:12,250 --> 00:36:13,500
to get plenty of rest, okay?

589
00:36:19,610 --> 00:36:20,820
People are looking.

590
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:36,650
I'm off.

591
00:36:47,690 --> 00:36:48,460
Depart!

592
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:54,780
I'll be back soon.

593
00:36:55,530 --> 00:36:56,690
I want to kiss you again.

594
00:37:00,980 --> 00:37:02,940
(Beilu Chengxiang)

595
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:14,340
(Tianlong Sect)

596
00:37:15,420 --> 00:37:16,130
Is it nice?

597
00:37:16,130 --> 00:37:16,730
Yes.

598
00:37:18,730 --> 00:37:19,420
Madam.

599
00:37:20,210 --> 00:37:21,340
What are these?

600
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:23,980
Master told us to prepare these.

601
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:25,900
This is a quilt.

602
00:37:26,130 --> 00:37:28,130
And these are new clothes,
shoes and hat.

603
00:37:34,690 --> 00:37:36,210
What else do you need?

604
00:37:36,210 --> 00:37:37,170
I'll prepare it.

605
00:37:38,610 --> 00:37:39,420
It's fine.

606
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:42,090
Hong, you guys can go.

607
00:37:42,690 --> 00:37:44,020
I want some time alone.

608
00:37:44,730 --> 00:37:45,570
Alright.

609
00:37:45,820 --> 00:37:47,610
This period is the hardest
on your sleep.

610
00:37:48,650 --> 00:37:49,980
We'll leave you then.

611
00:40:31,566 --> 00:40:35,326
♪Life passes by♪

612
00:40:36,606 --> 00:40:44,406
♪In the blink of an eye♪

613
00:40:45,006 --> 00:40:48,766
♪My heart is tied up♪

614
00:40:49,726 --> 00:40:53,806
♪By the unintentional worry♪

615
00:40:57,886 --> 00:41:01,946
♪What does the future hold?♪

616
00:41:02,846 --> 00:41:07,246
♪Hopefully, all wishes will be fulfilled♪

617
00:41:10,906 --> 00:41:14,986
♪What brings us together?♪

618
00:41:15,806 --> 00:41:21,666
♪Why are we going separate ways?♪

619
00:41:49,426 --> 00:41:55,306
♪I can never express love
and hate in words♪

620
00:41:55,306 --> 00:42:02,346
♪Going through all the winters in our lives♪

621
00:42:02,346 --> 00:42:08,066
♪Disposing of the unfulfilled wishes♪

622
00:42:08,066 --> 00:42:14,586
♪And keeping them all to myself♪

623
00:42:16,126 --> 00:42:21,586
♪Love only lasts so briefly♪

624
00:42:22,126 --> 00:42:28,186
♪Who do I waste my time for?♪

625
00:42:28,926 --> 00:42:34,186
♪Life is already full of debts♪

626
00:42:35,366 --> 00:42:41,586
♪So let's not dwell on the little time we have♪


